Show configuration help for 'usb PS3' controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t PS3 | more
Show configuration help for 'bluetooth PS3' controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c bluetooth -t PS3 | more
Configure 'bluetooth PS3' controller(s):confctrl_ph.sh -p prompt -t PS3
Go to 'Main' menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to 'Controllers' menu:ph_show_menu Controllers
Open Shell to home directory (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Return to previous screen:return
